@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lksvlc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.exp((v0 + 0.15 - tmp + 0.14)))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.46)
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.74) + tmp)
    v2 = (v1 / wp.cos(0.95))
    data[tid] = v0
